### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Create dev user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/dev/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sonali",
  "email": "sonali@example.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dev/users

### Add EC2 billing record
POST http://localhost:8080/api/billing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "usageDate": "2026-07-01",
  "service": "EC2",
  "resourceId": "i-12345",
  "region": "us-east-1",
  "cost": 12.50,
  "usageHours": 24,
  "cpuUtilization": 3.2
}

### Add RDS billing record
POST http://localhost:8080/api/billing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "usageDate": "2026-07-01",
  "service": "RDS",
  "resourceId": "db-prod-1",
  "region": "us-east-1",
  "cost": 35.80,
  "usageHours": 24,
  "cpuUtilization": 4.1
}

### Get billing records
GET http://localhost:8080/api/billing?userId=1

### Get total cost
GET http://localhost:8080/api/billing/total?userId=1

### Get cost by service
GET http://localhost:8080/api/billing/cost-by-service?userId=1

### Get idle resources
GET http://localhost:8080/api/billing/idle?userId=1
